1955;;A Lawless Street;;American;;Joseph H. Lewis;;Randolph Scott, Angela Lansbury;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Lawless_Street;;The marshal of Medicine Bend, Calem Ware (Randolph Scott), tries to keep peace in a lawless town whilst trying to prevent himself from being killed. The arrival of a show troupe reunites the marshal with someone from his past, leading to a showdown with his would-be killers and his old flame, Tally Dickinson (Angela Lansbury).